                        </foliation>
                        <foliation xml:id="modern">Modern pencilled Arabic numberals written upside-down on the lower-right corners of the b sides, which include the endpapers, hence not used for this record.</foliation>
                        <collation>Undetermined. Primarily quaternions throughout. 
